# Title

My Web Boilerplate - basic nodeJS server side render of pug client view with server side API support

## Installation

- Designed for NodeJS v20.16.0 and npm v10.8.1
- nvm instructions <https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm>
- install redis to use cachemanager <https://redis.io/docs/latest/operate/oss_and_stack/install/install-redis/install-redis-on-mac-os/>

## Starup

```bash
npm i
npm start
```

## Test Coverage

```bash
npm test
```

